Part 2: Learn SAP Navigation (Week 3–4)

Now learn how to use SAP system interface.

Learn these:

Login into SAP system

Understanding SAP GUI screen

Transaction codes (T-Codes)

Menu navigation

Creating favorites

Basic reports

Important T-Codes example:

VA01 – Create Sales Order

ME21N – Create Purchase Order

SE38 – Run programs

Goal:
You should be comfortable moving inside SAP system.
